<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<style>

table,th,td {
 border:1px solid black;
 border-cellspase:collapse;
 }
th,td {
padding:15px;
 }
</style>
</head>
</body>

<h2> cell padding<h2>
<p> cell padding specifies the space between the cell content and its borders.</p>

<table style="width:100%">
 <tr>
   <th>Firstname</th>
   <th>Lastname</th>
   <th>Age</th>
 </tr>
 <tr>
   <td>Sahel</td>
   <td>Ahmadi</td>
   <td>30</td>
 </tr>
 <tr>
 </table>
<p><strong>Tip:</strong> Try to change the padding to 5px.</p>

